title: Ambient Music Collection
description: A growing collection of ambient music tracks to contribute to your games' atmospheric desires
longDescription:
The Ambient Music Collection contains 23 tracks in this release version (1.0) and more are planned to be added in the future.

All tracks are seamless loops which span across a mixed variety of music genres, i.e. horror ambience, underwater ambience, monster ambience, mountain ambience and many more!


Listen to the full Playlist on Youtube - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5c85rXNaQg0&list=PLklRmOsWqTCbHMDuQFJyw7onRlTQLGu1H
